326678_7937188136319758_3777017794538859455_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=yyrBbvsMcL4Q7kNvgEVJYml&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBbmexltSAPdkjFOIZcBUPcAMQyJFfa3TQy87WsntXeaw&oe=67598705"}, "display_name": "Roblox taggers", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Game Description: Roblox Taggers\nTitle: Roblox Taggers\n\nGenre: Action, Casual, Multiplayer\n\nPlatform: vr\n\nDeveloper: hellovr1\n\n\n\nOverview\nRoblox Taggers is an exhilarating, fast-paced multiplayer game where players engage in the classic playground game of tag within a vibrant, interactive Roblox world. Inspired by the timeless fun of \"Goeill a Tag,\" this game takes the simple concept of tag and elevates it with dynamic environments, diverse characters, and unique abilities.\n\nGameplay\nObjective:\nPlayers are divided into two teams: Taggers and Runners. The Taggers' goal is to chase and tag all the Runners before the timer runs out. Runners must avoid being tagged and use the environment and power-ups to outmaneuver the Taggers.\n\nGame Modes:\n\nClassic Tag: Traditional tag mode where Taggers must tag all Runners to win.\nInfected Tag: Tagged players become Taggers, spreading the infection until only one Runner remains.\nFreeze Tag: Tagged players are frozen in place until a teammate unfreezes them. Taggers win by freezing all players.\nMaps:\n\nUrban Playground: Navigate through a bustling cityscape with rooftops, alleys, and parks.\nEnchanted Forest: A magical forest filled with hiding spots and mystical creatures.\nSpace Station: A futuristic environment with zero-gravity zones and space-themed obstacles.\nPower-Ups:\n\n\n\n", "short_description": "Roblox Taggers is a dynamic and exciting game on the Roblox platform, inspired by the classic playground game of tag. In this game, players are divided into two groups: Taggers and Runners. The Taggers' objective is to chase and tag as many Runners as possible within a set time limit, while the Runners aim 